OL,3,CWhich new laws could be scrapped
OL,4,Cbecause of the election?
OL,6,FBy Maya Bowles, ITV News Westminster
OL,7,FProducer
OL,9,FWith the shock announcement of a
OL,10,Fsurprise election on July 4, a number
OL,11,Fof key laws currently going through
OL,12,FParliament are likely to be scrapped.
OL,14,FParliament will be dissolved on
OL,15,FThursday, May 30 for six weeks until
OL,16,Fthe election, which means there's only
OL,17,Fa limited amount of time for laws to
OL,18,Fbe passed before Westminster turns
OL,19,Fit's attention to the election
OL,20,Fcampaigns.
